#include <iostream>
#include <vector>
#include <algorithm>

using namespace std;

typedef long long ll;
typedef pair<ll,ll> ii;
typedef vector<ii> vii;
typedef vector<ll> vi;

ll n,l;
vii cash;
vi sol;
vi cont;

bool calc(){
  for(int i = 0; i < n-1; ++i){
    if(cash[i+1].first%cash[i].first != 0) return false;
    cont[i] = (cash[i+1].first-1)/cash[i].first;
//     cout << i << ' ' << cont[i] << endl;
  }
  if(l%cash[n-1].first != cash[n-1].first-1 or l < cash[n-1].first) return false;
  cont[n-1] = l/cash[n-1].first;
  return true;
}

int main(){
  int t; cin >> t;
  for(int cass = 0; cass < t; ++cass){
    cin >> n >> l;
    cash = vii(n);
    for(int i = 0; i < n; ++i){ cin >> cash[i].first; cash[i].second = i; }
    sort(cash.begin(), cash.end());
    cont = sol = vi(n,0);
    if(cash[0].first != 1) cout << -1 << '\n';
    else{
      if(calc()){
	for(int i = 0; i < n; ++i){
	  sol[cash[i].second] = cont[i];
	}
	for(int i = 0; i < n; ++i){
	  if(i) cout << ' ';
	  cout << sol[i];
	}
	cout << '\n';
      }
      else{
	cout << -1 << '\n';
      }
    }
  }
}
